x4freetext: The excitation functions of the this reaction  was
derived from the thick target yield.
Resonance widths are given, but they are the raw
experimental values; in particular, the width of the
incident proton spectrum and the thickness of the
targets have not been taken into account.

x4code.headerHelp: Error in value of quantity, defined under ERR-ANALYS

x4freetext: This relatively large uncertainty has two
components essentially related to the imprecision
with which one can determine on the one hand the
concentration of sodium in the implanted area on the
other hand the true intensity of the incident beam.
